eva

Interface Entity


  • public interface Entity
    Provides Entity/Object-oriented access to database-entities. Entities are lazy: value of attributes are retrieved on-demand when get(Object) or touch() are called. After retrieval attribute-values are cached inside the entity.

    Entities are equal if they have the same entity-id and equivalent databases.
